{"tid":376860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港再被超越]深圳女上地鐵電梯突塌渠蓋 跌入集水井受傷","createTime":"2017-08-27T09:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T12:14:21.000Z","uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"309b74541461bb3dfb423890ce23c32f8e71848e","tid":376860,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170827/large/1503806248_4b01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170827%2Flarge%2F1503806248_4b01.jpg&h=d2791f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 昨日上午10時許，一名深圳女乘客在地鐵3號線翠竹站C出口通道電扶梯前準備出站時，因踏上損壞的井蓋板而跌入集水井中，同行乘客及其他乘客立即合力將她拉起。事發後，車站人員立即趕到現場並陪同其前往醫院就醫。經醫院檢查，受傷乘客手部、腿部等處擦傷，經醫院處理後暫無大礙已出院。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生後，深圳地鐵當局全線檢查電梯集水井蓋板，並對事件中受傷的乘客誠摯致歉，對在事件中及時施以援手的乘客表示感謝。同時，針對此次事件的發生，當局將在查明原因，展開調查，必要時會向涉事單位問責。"},{"pid":"bdf85cbfaa03833b33d3b42ae5c449f3c6aa85a0","tid":376860,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:54:01.000Z","msg":"附合國情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5d72d0150ecd546b641b46fd0c717ee42b082f","tid":376860,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"港資相關？唔好跟車太貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69ef1073ae4b0c1baab4b46eeed2efe9eb04f8b","tid":376860,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:57:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港資相關？唔好跟車太貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3號線唔係龜鐵營運"},{"pid":"68ff51ed939fb7771fa0804aae8a9e49cc14cb71","tid":